# Onboarding Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create onboarding (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/onboardings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "candidateId": "<candidate-id>"
}

### Get all onboardings (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/onboardings
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get onboarding by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/onboardings/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update onboarding (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/onboardings/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### Delete onboarding (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/onboardings/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
